@HostAddress = http://localhost:5237

### ---------------- AUTHENTICATION ---------------- ###

### Register Admin User
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@vtclbd.com",
  "password": "Admin@123!"
}

### Login
# @name loginRequest
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@vtclbd.com",
  "password": "Admin@123!"
}

### Extract Token (Visual Studio / VS Code REST Client format)
@authToken = {{loginRequest.response.body.$.data.token}}


### ---------------- COURSE MANAGEMENT ---------------- ###

### Create Course
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/course
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Advanced Interior Design",
  "description": "Learn modern interior design principles.",
  "price": 49.99,
  "videoUrl": "https://cloudinary.com/video123",
  "instructorName": "Jane Doe",
  "isPublished": true
}

### Get All Courses
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/course
Accept: application/json

### ---------------- PROJECT SHOWCASE ---------------- ###

### Create Project
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/project
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Skyline Commercial Building",
  "description": "A 20-story commercial tower in downtown.",
  "imageUrl": "https://cloudinary.com/image123",
  "category": "Construction",
  "clientName": "Skyline Corp",
  "location": "New York, USA",
  "isPublished": true
}

### Get All Projects
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/project
Accept: application/json

### ---------------- PAYMENT & ENROLLMENT ---------------- ###

### Dummy Payment (Enroll in Course)
# Replace courseId with a real one
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/payment/pay-dummy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "courseId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### ---------------- CONTENT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM (CMS) ---------------- ###

### Create Content Block
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/cms
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "identifier": "home-hero-title",
  "content": "Master The Art of Building and Engineering",
  "type": "Text",
  "isActive": true
}

### Get All Content Blocks
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/cms
Accept: application/json

### Get Content Block by Identifier
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/cms/home-hero-title
Accept: application/json

### ---------------- COURSE MODULES & LESSONS ---------------- ###

### Create Module
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/coursemodule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "courseId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "title": "Getting Started",
  "description": "Introduction and setup",
  "order": 1,
  "isPublished": true
}

### Add Lesson to Module
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/coursemodule/lessons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "moduleId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "title": "Welcome & Overview",
  "videoUrl": "https://cloudinary.com/video/sample",
  "durationInSeconds": 300,
  "order": 1,
  "isPublished": true
}

### Add Resource Link to Module
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/coursemodule/resources
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "moduleId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "title": "Course Notes PDF",
  "url": "https://example.com/notes.pdf",
  "type": "PDF"
}

### Get Modules for a Course
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/coursemodule/by-course/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### ---------------- PROGRESS & CERTIFICATES ---------------- ###

### Mark Lesson as Complete
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/progress/mark-complete
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "lessonId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Get Course Progress
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/progress/course/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Certificate (auto-issued on 100% completion)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/progress/certificate/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}



